---

- Mission Control cockpit: **Radar View** (default) · **Kanban View** tabs; state (scope, KPI focus, selection) preserved across tabs.
- Zone 1 left Operational Snapshot · Zone 2 hero Radar · Zone 3 Opportunity Preview **slide-over** (collapsed by default; never permanently shrinks Radar).
- Radar blip hover = tooltip; **single click** = open Preview drawer; **double click** = Opportunity Workspace.
- KPI click → expand collapsible opportunity list (one at a time; independently scrollable).
- Radar dots use collision-safe placement — never overlap.
- Quadrant labels **outside** the dial; Kanban is primary only in Kanban View (not stacked under Radar).
- Follow Enterprise UX, Layout Integrity, Data Integrity, and Metric SSOT standards.
- **Real-time:** `subscribeLoanFilesUpdated` + 60s poll / `storage` fallback.
- Never change Operational Vector / health scoring when adjusting layout chrome.
- Never show Rejected / Lost / Cancelled / Withdrawn / Closed lenders on Radar cards.
- Prefer Active Workspace / Opportunity Workspace from Kanban cards and Preview actions.
- Matrix screen is **retired**. Do not restore Matrix.
- Four quadrants: **On Track** (N) · **Follow-up Required** (E) · **At Risk** (S) · **Needs Attention** (W).
- Kanban cards **never** draggable.